  the 
  <express_ref linkend="product_environment_definition:arm:Product_environment_definition_arm.Environment_definition_view"/>
  in which the product is supported or operates.
</ext_description>

<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_environment_definition_arm  Entity: Environment_assignment  Attribute: item 
   <express_ref linkend="product_environment_definition:arm:Product_environment_definition_arm.Environment_assignment.item"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
<ext_description linkend="Product_environment_definition_arm.Environment_assignment.item">
  the product that is or planned to be operating in the environment.  
</ext_description>

